Kung hindi mo mamasamain,

00:16:21.800 --> 00:16:23.050
Tawagin mo na lang akong Panginoon Sanlai.

00:16:23.050 --> 00:16:24.400
tulad ng lahat.

00:16:30.880 --> 00:16:32.480
Ikaw ba talaga 'yung gabing 'yun?

